## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-314">Il <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> codifica di un buffer di caratteri in una sola volta, anziché un carattere.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-314">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> encodes a buffer of characters all at once, rather than character by character.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-315">Viene generata un'eccezione quando il <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Flush%2A> metodo viene chiamato se vengono rilevati errori di codifica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-315">An exception is thrown when the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Flush%2A> method is called if any encoding errors are encountered.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-316">Il <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> proprietà si applica solo al <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> le istanze vengono create con l'oggetto specificato <xref:System.IO.Stream> o con il nome file specificato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-316">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> property only applies to the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instances that are created either with the specified <xref:System.IO.Stream> or with the specified file name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-317">Se il <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> istanza viene creata con l'oggetto specificato <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>, <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> viene eseguito l'override di proprietà per la codifica dell'oggetto sottostante <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-317">If the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instance is created with the specified <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>, the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> property is overridden by the encoding of the underlying <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-318">Ad esempio, se questa proprietà è impostata su Unicode (UTF-16) per un particolare <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>, ma il writer sottostante è un <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter> (che deriva da <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>) con la codifica impostata su UTF8, l'output sarà con codificata UTF-8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-318">For example, if this property is set to Unicode (UTF-16) for a particular <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>, but the underlying writer is a <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter> (which derives from <xref:System.IO.TextWriter>) with its encoding set to UTF8, the output will be UTF-8 encoded.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-319">Se il <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> con altri parametri di output, viene creata l'istanza di <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> proprietà viene ignorata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-319">If the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instance is created with other output parameters, the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> property is ignored.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-320">Nell'esempio seguente:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-320">In the following example:</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-321">Il valore predefinito di <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> è `Encoding.UTF8`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-321">The default value of <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> is `Encoding.UTF8`.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-322">Il <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter> è impostata su `Encoding.Unicode` e <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter>codifica sostituzioni di <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> impostazione.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-322">The <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter> is set to `Encoding.Unicode` and the <xref:System.IO.StreamWriter>’s encoding overrides the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings.Encoding%2A> setting.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-323">L'output sarà `Encoding.Unicode`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-323">The output will be `Encoding.Unicode`.</span></span>  

```csharp  
using (StreamWriter output =  
    new StreamWriter(new FileStream("Xml01.xml", FileMode.Create), Encoding.Unicode))  
{  
    using (XmlWriter xmlWriter =  
        XmlWriter.Create(output, new XmlWriterSettings()))  
    {  
        xmlWriter.WriteStartDocument();  
        xmlWriter.WriteStartElement("Root");  
        xmlWriter.WriteEndElement();  
        xmlWriter.WriteEndDocument();  
    }  
}  
```  

> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="65d5b-324">Non accettare un <xref:System.Text.Encoding> oggetto da un'origine non attendibile.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65d5b-324">Do not accept an <xref:System.Text.Encoding> object from an untrusted source.</span></span>  



